    <div class="newbody body parsys">

<div class="parbase image slate_image section">


 <div class="">
        <figure class="image inline " style="width: 590px;  display: block;margin: 0 auto;float: none;"> <img title="150204_TV_BroadCity204" alt="Broad City" src="/content/dam/slate/articles/arts/television/2015/02/150204_TV_BroadCity204.jpg.CROP.promovar-mediumlarge.jpg" > <figcaption class="caption"><span>Bob Balaban and Abbi Jacobson.<em></em></span></figcaption>  <p class="credit">Photo courtesy Ali Goldstein/Comedy Central</p> 
        </figure>
        </div>
        <script>
        requirejs(["jquery"], function($) {
            if ($(window).width() < 640) {
                $(".slate_image figure").width("100%");
            }
        });
        </script> </div>

<div class="text text-1 parbase section">

<p>Wednesday night&rsquo;s<em> </em><a href="http://www.amazon.com/dp/B00JBKKMNU/?tag=slatmaga-20"><em>Broad City</em></a> continued the show&rsquo;s exploration of <a href="http://www.slate.com/blogs/xx_factor/2015/01/14/broad_city_season_premiere_abbi_and_ilana_return_with_an_episode_about_friendship.html">sexual role reversals</a> with a rare televised pegging. (That would be the <a href="http://www.thestranger.com/seattle/SavageLove?oid=7730">term Dan Savage coined</a>, in 2001, to mean &ldquo;a woman fucking a man in the ass with a strap-on dildo.&rdquo;) Here&rsquo;s how it went down: At long last, Abbi has scored a date with her dreamy neighbor, Jeremy, and she finds herself intoxicated by his musky persona. They spend the evening sipping his homebrewed cider beer, discussing his travels with his terminally ill dog, gazing at his woodwork, and finally, engaging in passionate sex. When Abbi asks if he wants to &ldquo;maybe switch,&rdquo; she means she&rsquo;s ready to move on from missionary; he assumes that she&rsquo;s interested in strapping on a dildo and pegging him in the ass with it, and eagerly presents her with a neon-green phallus bound to a leather harness.</p>


</div>




